{"tha-ap352:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap352:0.2":"Ekapadumiyavagga ","tha-ap352:0.3":"Ekanjaliyattheraapadana ","tha-ap352:1.1":"“Romaso nama sambuddho, ","tha-ap352:1.2":"nadikule vasi tada; ","tha-ap352:1.3":"Addasam virajam buddham, ","tha-ap352:1.4":"pitaramsimva bhanumam. ","tha-ap352:2.1":"Ukkamukhapahatthamva, ","tha-ap352:2.2":"khadirangarasannibham; ","tha-ap352:2.3":"Osadhimva virocantam, ","tha-ap352:2.4":"ekanjalimakasaham. ","tha-ap352:3.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap352:3.2":"yam anjalimakasaham; ","tha-ap352:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap352:3.4":"anjaliya idam phalam. ","tha-ap352:4.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap352:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap352:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap352:5.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma ekanjaliyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap352:6.1":"Ekanjaliyattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap352:7.1":"Ekapadumiyavaggo pancatimsatimo. ","tha-ap352:8.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap352:9.1":"Padumi uppalamali, ","tha-ap352:9.2":"dhajo kinkanikam nalam; ","tha-ap352:9.3":"Campako padumo mutthi, ","tha-ap352:9.4":"tindukekanjali tatha; ","tha-ap352:9.5":"Cha ca satthi ca gathayo, ","tha-ap352:9.6":"ganitayo vibhavibhi. "}